data.description: Adorable and charming home in downtown Circleville! Home offers hardwood floors, arched doorways , a decorative fireplace, and so much more. However, home is also in need of repairs and is being sold as is, where is. So it is encouraged for the buyer to read the property disclosure form and attend the open houses. Open house dates are: 2/18/2024 1:30-3:00pm, 2/25/2024 2-4pm,3/03/2024 3:30-5:00pm Property is being sold at an online AUCTION with a minimum bid of $120,000. Auction to take place March 4 2024-March 8 2024
